 \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41367,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/10\/05\/sinking-until-yawm-al-qiyamah\/","url_meta":{"origin":17581,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Proud man sinking into earth until Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA man among those before you went out haughtily in his fine garment, so Allah ordered the earth to seize him. He is sinking into it until the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2491\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19346,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/17\/allah-shade-relief\/","url_meta":{"origin":17581,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shade: Allah shades those who give relief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever grants respite to someone in difficulty or relieves him, Allah will shade him on the Day of Resurrection when there is no shade but His.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1306 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousn